* Only the reference type parameter (BigDecimal) methods are actually * implemented. The methods with the primitive parameters (double) should * create a BigDecimal and then delegate to the primitive methods * (and do nothing else). * If possible the implementations should be pure BigDecimal arithmatic * without rounding.
